      "title": "Basil goes to work",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A discussion has been held between the Kandy District Members of Parliament and other political representatives of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna. This discussion was held at the party headquarters of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna under the chairmanship of former minister Basil Rajapaksa.",
        "Members of Parliament Namal Rajapaksa, Dilum Amunugama, Rohitha Abeygunawardena, Sagara Kariyawasam, Mr. Mahindananda Aluthgamage and others joined for this."
      ],
